content: ncale: Merged 4 PRs this month, including a significant refactoring of Telegram markdown parsing in PR #4279 (+63718/-10114 lines) and adding a typing indicator to Telegram in PR #4280 (+1286/-212 lines). Also contributed to message button functionality (PR #4187) and fixed Telegram type exposure (PR #4287), with activity spread across 7 days. Provided 1 code review and made 3 PR comments, primarily focusing on feature work (47%) and documentation improvements (39%).
